headline.print_headline: At 60, Newport Jazz Fest Looks to the Future
headline.main: At 60, Newport Jazz Fest Looks to the Future

lead_paragraph: Newport Jazz Festival founder George Wein is more interested in where jazz is going than in where it's been as he marks the 60th anniversary of the granddaddy of all outdoor jazz festivals.
